---
title: Fully Loaded Beef Taquitos with Pico de Gallo, Creamy Guacamole & Hot Sauce
description: When we’re in the mood to mix things up, we love taquitos, also known as rolled-up tacos with a crispy outer shell. We achieve the taquito crunch factor by baking the stuffed tortillas—full of zesty pork and a blend of Mexican cheeses—no messy deep frying required. That golden crust is the perfect canvas for pico de gallo, creamy guacamole, and hot sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6422f817c48c491a110e73ff-f2a4fb0c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6501e9cbf0fc6956c436708c.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
servings: 2
author: Michelle Doll Olson
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/fully-loaded-beef-taquitos-6501e9cbf0fc6956c436708c
cuisine: Mexican
nutrition:
  calories: 1020 kcal
